    <item>
      <title>罗杰斯接近达成 51 亿美元网络融资协议 股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/rogers-nears-5-1-billion-financing-deal-with-unnamed-investor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大最大的无线通讯公司罗杰斯通讯公司 (Rogers Communications Inc.) 表示，它已接近完成一项 70 亿加元（51 亿美元）的结构性股权投资，用于资助其部分网络并减少其债务负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/rogers-nears-5-1-billion-financing-deal-with-unnamed-investor</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 11:29:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
